            <img src="/carbidesaws-rebuild/brand-freud.png" alt="Freud Tools" class="h-20 w-auto object-contain brightness-150" />
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.whitesiderouterbits.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex-shrink-0 hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
